== [    BASIC ] ============================================================================================
   MNEMONIC: call [ENC: DEFAULT, MAP: DEFAULT, OPC: 0xFF]
     LENGTH:  2
        SSZ: 64
       EOSZ: 64
       EASZ: 64
   CATEGORY: CALL
    ISA-SET: I86
    ISA-EXT: BASE
 EXCEPTIONS: NONE
 ATTRIBUTES: HAS_MODRM ACCEPTS_BND ACCEPTS_NOTRACK 
  OPTIMIZED: FF D0 

== [ OPERANDS ] ============================================================================================
##       TYPE  VISIBILITY  ACTION      ENCODING   SIZE  NELEM  ELEMSZ  ELEMTYPE                        VALUE
--  ---------  ----------  ------  ------------   ----  -----  ------  --------  ---------------------------
 0   REGISTER    EXPLICIT       R      MODRM_RM     64      1      64       INT                          rax
 1   REGISTER      HIDDEN      RW          NONE     64      1      64       INT                          rip
 2   REGISTER      HIDDEN      RW          NONE     64      1      64       INT                          rsp
 3     MEMORY      HIDDEN       W          NONE     64      1      64       INT  TYPE  =                 MEM
                                                                                 SEG   =                  ss
                                                                                 BASE  =                 rsp
                                                                                 INDEX =                none
                                                                                 SCALE =                   0
                                                                                 DISP  =  0x0000000000000000
--  ---------  ----------  ------  ------------   ----  -----  ------  --------  ---------------------------

== [      ATT ] ============================================================================================
   ABSOLUTE: call *%rax
   RELATIVE: call *%rax

== [    INTEL ] ============================================================================================
   ABSOLUTE: call rax
   RELATIVE: call rax

== [ SEGMENTS ] ============================================================================================
FF D0 
:  :..MODRM
:..OPCODE
